"You'd be surprised what you can learn by dealing with races outside 
Cybertronian space."  Gatara lets the comment hang as she beckons him 
down a corridor.  "Let's find some place to talk, shall we?"  This is 
about as close to flirting as the croc-bot usually gets.

Riekan carries Jayde - who protests all the while that she can walk 
on her own - down a different hall to the med-bay.  Meanwhile, 
Devilcat turns to Noir, Fury, and Torin.  "You three come with me.  
We've got some business to take care of."
